claim.claim-text:
A method, comprising:
impinging a plurality of particles (305, 205) on a target (110, 210, 310) such that electrons (120) are emitted from the target (110, 210, 310);
transporting the electrons (120) from the target (110, 210, 310) to a heat sink (140) through a transporting medium (130, 330), wherein the target (110, 210, 310) and the heat sink (140) are separated by a distance (130, 147);
cooling the electrons (120) using the heat sink (140); and
returning the electrons (120) from the heat sink (140) to the target (110, 210, 310).
